name: Hard Times Come And Go
author: Pokey LaFarge
lyrics:
Whoooooaaaaa
We were brothers, just like Kane and Abel.
Hard times come and go so we're told.
You took my money, left the pennies on the table.
Hard times come and go so we're told.
They're a snake in the grass, an owl in the trees,
and they'll swoop down upon you, and bring you down to your knees.
I recall these words I was told. Hard times come, hard times go.
But now they're harder than they've ever been before,
and I don't know if I can take them anymore.
